commit.message:
Support RSpec 4

RSpec 4 has changed the semantic of multi-condition filtering.
To include a module to a group matching *any* of the conditions, the
conditions should be separate statements.
replaced supported/ unsupported versions of Ruby
updated ci settings.
updated to catch up rails 6 and ruby 3
updated to pass with Ruby 3.0

Pass source to template separatedly.

This fixes compatibility with ActionView 6.0.0+, whic deprecated old
style template handlers [[1]].

Fixes #61.

[1]: https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/35119
